test_all_zero_range:
assert [1, 3, 5] == []
  Left contains 3 more items, first extra item: 1
  Full diff:
  - []
  + [1, 3, 5]
test_odd_range:
assert [1, 3, 5] == [121, 121, 12...121, 121, ...]
  At index 0 diff: 1 != 121
  Right contains 4 more items, first extra item: 121
  Full diff:
  - [121, 121, 121, 121, 121, 121, 121]
  + [1, 3, 5]
